<HEADLINE> India Foils Pakistani Infiltration Bids </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Three infiltrators were killed in an exchange of fire with
Indian troops near the Assempur border outpost in the Samba sub-
sector, it added.
</P>
<P>
Earlier Indian troops foiled another infiltration bid in the
Manjakot area of Poonch district gunning down three near LoC.
</P>
<P>
They also shot dead three of the 14 Pakistani militants who
tried to cross over to India into the Saujian area of Poonch
sector. 
