<HEADLINE> Dutch Beats Denmark, Moves to Quarterfinals </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
BRUSSELS, June 16 (Xinhua) -- The Netherlands downed Denmark 3-
0 in Rotterdam to cruise into the quarterfinal of the European
Championship on Friday, taking France with it and eliminating the
Danes and the Czech Republic.
</P>
<P>
Patrick Kluivert put the Dutch lead in the 58th minute.
Substitute Ronald de Boer added the second in the 66th and
Boudewijn Zenden scored the third with 12 minutes left. 
