the poverty line, and over 80 percent of the Ugandans are
farmers.
</P>
<P>
He encouraged the people to move away from traditional ways of
farming and adopt modern methods of carrying on agriculture.
</P>
<P>
The NRM government has initiated the programme of posting
agriculture, forestry and veterinary experts at every sub-county
level to advise farmers on the proper use of fertilizers,
irrigation and improved seeds to ensure better returns for every
household, said Museveni.
</P>
<P>
