<HEADLINE> Wang Beats Koyama at Japan Open Table Tennis Tourney </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TOKYO, June 17 (Xinhua) -- World champion Wang Nan of China
overcame a scare to beat Japan's Chire Koyama in the women's
