in Kobe on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
Wang, who defeated Koyama in last year's final, staged a
comeback from 16-19 down in the final game to seal a 18-21, 21-14,
21-16, 16-21, 21-19 victory over Koyama.
</P>
<P>
In the semi-finals Sunday, top-seeded Wang will take on Ryu Ji-
Hye of South Korea, a 21-19, 21-19, 21-13 winner over Sun Jin of
China.
</P>
<P>
