Linghui, who defeated Liu Guozheng 21-14, 21-17, 21-12 in an all-
Chinese match.
</P>
<P>
Cheung Yuk of Hong Kong, China scored a 21-18, 21-17, 20-22, 21-
19 victory over Chuan Chin-yuan of Chinese Taipei to set up a semi-
final meeting against 1998 Asian champion Wang Liqin of China.
</P>
<P>
Wang, second seed, eliminated the last European player, Daimien
Eloi of France, 21-18, 21-13, 21-15. 
