<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, June 17 (Xinhua) -- Thai Foreign Minister Surin
Pitsuwan will visit Singapore next week, aimed at strengthening
ties and cooperation between the two neighboring countries, the
Thai News Agency (TNA) reported Saturday.
</P>
